HEADWORD: Alexandrian
<hw>Al`ex*an"dri*an</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>Of or pertaining to Alexandria in Egypt; <as>as, the
<ex>Alexandrian</ex> library</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Applied to a kind of heroic verse. See
<er>Alexandrine</er>, <pos>n.</pos></def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Alexandrine</ent>⟦br⟧
